Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:59.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}The Monstrous Washikamigiri's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs195\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,725.389)}Human Hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, we're going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading for the summit of Mount Omuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those annoying kids roped me into this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and now then they want\Nto run off by themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we should get some lunch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you eat so much, Choco?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But fall is about food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want mine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mountain called?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mount Togasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! I need a ten-yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for the\Nhotel shuttle to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe my eyes were playing tricks on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keita, watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you guys see\Nsomething weird over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keita, you need to watch\Nwhere you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I saw it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like a yellow board,\Nbut then it took a human shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How long to the Tokyu Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that smoke coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mountain fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Keita, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right. This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get under the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Gel Shocker cyborg Washikamigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans are my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture every one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Human Hunt was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this method to acquire\Na large number of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not let anyone who\Nwitnesses your plan go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have traps everywhere.\NThey will not escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I want to see the begonias!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't get time off very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's no way for the\NRider Corps Captain to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a nice, relaxing bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be safe now, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those scary people we saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They look just like the one\NI saw through the telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Someone's there!\N- Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm caught in this trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to bear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What wonderful water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since\Nwe relaxed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to wear\Nyour clothes in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just asked at the front\Ndesk. They're in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A hotel shuttle that left Mount Omuro\Ntwo hours ago hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to see the\Nbegonias in the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I hear they're 50,000 yen apiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wonder if this one's edible!\N- 50,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Learned anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the people are missing, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's it looking like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The microbus' engine is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't a breakdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, I say we split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll check this way.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, let's go to that lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go in for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for this.\N- It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a monster heading this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure out something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My papa was taken by a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid... could you tell me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker really is behind this, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider Kid Corps\Ncan't let this stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll save your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Taki and Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't called back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I contact them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want the enemy to\Npick up our transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we preserve the humans in this form,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have them at our disposal\Nwhenever we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Divide them into those to be made into\Nmonsters and those to be made into combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After we modify them, victory will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget your other mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I will remove the Kamen\NRider's head with my scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:51.92,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm caught in a trap! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course.\N- Help me out, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Use the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki's caught in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Gel Shocker's Washikamigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be Taki, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught a bigger prey than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? You're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll foam you into a cocoon. Rest well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hold it!\N- Taki, this one will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your opponent, Washikamigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you all off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of my feather missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot... I feel hot all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I combine the powers of\Nan eagle and a mantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally finished Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't celebrate just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure until\Nwe find Rider's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Combatants, find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Free the humans preserved in your foam,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and modify them into combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Perform the modification surgery at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One of his feathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Apply the restoration fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.63,Italics,,0,0,0,,Modifying people to suit their purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:17.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,Just like they did to me, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I escaped before\Nthey modified my brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,I need to stop that\Nsurgery, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart rate has dropped by thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to staunch the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Head incision complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to remove the heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Rider, you survived?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri, it seems you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will defeat Rider for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not return here until Rider is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... let's step outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri! Tear Rider's\Nhead from his shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:51.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:54.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:05.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.97,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:34.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:41.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:45.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:48.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:52.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:59.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:03.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:07.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, it's nothing, really.\N- I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo! Say hi to the\NKamen Rider for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to go, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:01.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Washikamigiri's terrible plan was foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:05.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker would return\Nwith more mysterious schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,70,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.14,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A deliveryman of doom\Nappears from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:20.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's when I, the great\NSpiderlion, show my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The deliveryman of doom\Nis whispering again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:28.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Kill Kamen Rider soon!" it says!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:31.16,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx86\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Gel Shocker's Deliveryman of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:50.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:57.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:05.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:09.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Washikamigiri's Human Hunt
Comment: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's Deliveryman of Death!